{"tid":254402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實 m 記 d 23 蚊餐賣得咁平有冇錢賺嫁？","createTime":"2017-05-23T07:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:09:10.000Z","uid":30922,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba07fa5bf4256f74434a08c9973eb7c9b48e42e2","tid":254402,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"用麥樂雞做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 麥樂雞當佢成本 $2 一件 <br />\n6 件加埋都 $12<br />\n<br />\n2. 可樂 出面賣都要 $6 罐<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $5 好未 ???<br />\n<br />\n3. 薯條 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大包咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $5 包 (中薯條咋，加大另計)<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有茄汁呀 麥樂雞醬呀 <br />\n有時預到 d 比較小家既人又要比多幾包茄汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到預 $2<br />\n<br />\nTotal Cost = $12 + $5 + $5 + $2 <br />\n= $24 &gt; $23<br />\n<br />\n仲未計埋 d 燈油火蠟 咁賣法 m 記咪蝕住黎做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁多年黎係咁加價都唔係冇道理喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffbf2ea2661ca1a367ba3d6a0b59ee789af5603","tid":254402,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"又回帶 好悶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da42a5c6ec554b1a309b96dd84dfc6d5e6fb8102","tid":254402,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"冇，幾年前做過經理，果陣已經蝕住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家就算quit左，去幫襯都盡量少買特價餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797ec9f559681c98831d5e9e80e40b99ed858f14","tid":254402,"uid":19646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"邊到有$23餐買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345b43485ccf6da62097a62a5d86baefd2d5cd82","tid":254402,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到有$23餐買<img src=\"/assets/faces/no